00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:34,650
don't spread it around.

288
00:16:35,510 --> 00:16:36,600
A couple of nights ago,

289
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,080
Young Mr. He called me.

290
00:16:38,670 --> 00:16:39,670
He told me

291
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,000
he was injured.

292
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:42,670
He...

293
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,500
That's all he said.

294
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:48,840
He is drunk.

295
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:50,790
Do I need to bring them to you

296
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:52,390
so you can ask them yourself?

297
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,200
No need.

298
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,220
That's enough.

299
00:16:54,790 --> 00:16:55,440
Okay.

300
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,770
Why don't you talk to your brother?

301
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,960
Sometimes you need to swallow your pride.

302
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:06,030
What's more important, business or family?

303
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:06,960
If this continues,

304
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:08,290
you won't last, either.

305
00:17:09,440 --> 00:17:10,160
Fine.

306
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,220
I'll have a good talk with my brother.

307
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:16,960
About who's next

308
00:17:18,720 --> 00:17:20,270
after I'm dead.

309
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:28,720
Buddy.

310
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:31,680
I should thank you.

311
00:17:33,720 --> 00:17:35,920
If it weren't for those hits you gave me,

312
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,680
I would have lived

313
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,350
my whole life in confusion.

314
00:18:28,310 --> 00:18:28,960
Muzhi.

315
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,510
Gang?

316
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:33,600
Are you okay?

317
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:34,830
Don't worry, Muzhi.

318
00:18:37,410 --> 00:18:38,510
Your brother has gotten into trouble.

319
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,830
The police are watching him now.

320
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,180
He can't leave Hanzhou, either.

321
00:18:41,180 --> 00:18:42,900
I'll keep an eye on him for you.

322
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,070
Liu Tianye.

323
00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:49,080
If you lay a hand on Gang,

324
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:52,080
you're forcing my hand.

325
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,000
That's right.

326
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,680
Lin's case has caused such a big mess.

327
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,510
I know you don't want to admit defeat.

328
00:18:58,510 --> 00:18:59,510
And you want to drag me down with you,

329
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:00,030
right?

330
00:19:00,830 --> 00:19:02,570
But now I have your brother.

331
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:05,410
What cards do you have left to play?

332
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:06,830
I'm advising you

333
00:19:07,600 --> 00:19:09,110
to just focus on your business

334
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:10,240
and earn some money for your brother

335
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,440
so he can get away.

336
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:14,090
Don't touch my family.

337
00:19:16,690 --> 00:19:17,820
Let's meet and talk.

338
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:19,800
Just you and me, one on one.

339
00:19:19,800 --> 00:19:20,730
I'll be waiting.

340
00:19:35,070 --> 00:19:35,750
Tianye,

341
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,400
they have no cards left to play.

342
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,400
Are we still going to play with them?

343
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:42,010
He knows too much about us.

344
00:19:42,550 --> 00:19:44,680
Keeping him around is always trouble.

345
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,550
Let's talk first if possible.

346
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:47,750
If that doesn't work,

347
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,940
we'll take care of him.

348
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:53,360
Alright.

349
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:27,240
Sir,

350
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:31,030
how's the investigation going?

351
00:20:31,030 --> 00:20:32,830
The Anti-Smuggling Bureau found nothing.

352
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:35,630
Longwan Logistics has already
moved everything.

353
00:20:37,510 --> 00:20:38,440
What about Gang?

354
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:39,510
Don't worry.

355
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:41,550
I've found leads on him.

356
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:42,890
Wait for my update.

357
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:43,750
Okay.

358
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,480
War has broken out between the two sides.

359
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,480
No matter how their fight turns out,

360
00:21:01,590 --> 00:21:02,650
keep an eye on them.

361
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,510
Be ready at any time.

362
00:21:05,070 --> 00:21:06,720
Cut ties if things go wrong.

363
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:08,030
Copy that.

364
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,290
What did you want to say
by calling me out here?

365
00:21:29,290 --> 00:21:33,880
[Ancestral Hall
of the Liu, Wen, and Qin Families]

366
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:34,880
Nothing special.

367
00:21:35,330 --> 00:21:36,310
It's just that recently,

368
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:38,970
so many things have happened
one after another.

369
00:21:41,480 --> 00:21:44,590
I remembered how hard it was
for us in Longwan

370
00:21:47,110 --> 00:21:49,040
and how difficult our journey was.

371
00:21:52,110 --> 00:21:53,240
I'm just afraid

372
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:58,240
our family might fall apart.

373
00:22:03,350 --> 00:22:04,030
Jiangyan.

374
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,920
Can you do me a favor?

375
00:22:12,590 --> 00:22:13,270
What is it?

376
00:22:46,160 --> 00:22:46,750
Jiangyan,

377
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:47,480
you're back?

378
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:48,530
It's so late.

379
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,920
You're still up?

380
00:22:50,350 --> 00:22:51,750
The meeting is tomorrow.

381
00:22:54,450 --> 00:22:55,450
I hope

382
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:58,310
everything gets better after tomorrow.

383
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:01,490
I love looking at your childhood photos.

384
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:02,880
So adorable.

385
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:08,930
What's on your mind, Jiangyan?

386
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,070
Mom,

387
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:16,080
I'm planning to marry Jiajun

388
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,030
once this is all over.

389
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,550
Jiajun

390
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,130
is pretty good to me.

391
00:23:24,070 --> 00:23:25,640
That's wonderful!

392
00:23:28,310 --> 00:23:28,920
Jiangyan.

393
00:23:29,350 --> 00:23:29,960
Hurry up.

394
00:23:30,480 --> 00:23:30,960
Here.

395
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:31,970
Open it and see.

396
00:23:32,310 --> 00:23:32,960
Open it.

397
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:38,350
Try it on.

398
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:40,400
Come on.

399
00:23:44,350 --> 00:23:45,750
Isn't it too small for me?

400
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:47,550
No, it's not. Try it on.

401
00:23:48,070 --> 00:23:48,550
Slowly.

402
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:52,030
It actually fits.

403
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,000
How beautiful.

404
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:56,030
It's lovely,

405
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,440
really lovely.

406
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:04,140
It doesn't look as nice as
when my mom wore it when she was young.

407
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,250
You still remember, right?

408
00:24:08,830 --> 00:24:10,200
This bracelet

409
00:24:10,200 --> 00:24:12,640
was given to your mother

410
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:15,440
by your grandmother when she got married.

411
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:18,530
I think today it can be passed on to you.

412
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,720
She would be so happy.

413
00:24:23,110 --> 00:24:24,840
That little girl from back then

414
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:27,270
has grown up now.

415
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:29,880
I can tell her

416
00:24:30,590 --> 00:24:32,120
I've completed my mission.

417
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:34,730
I've raised your daughter

418
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:36,270
into

419
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:39,880
a beautiful, elegant young lady.

420
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:42,540
Thank you, Mom.

421
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:45,130
That's wonderful.

422
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:47,750
Mom.

423
00:24:49,110 --> 00:24:50,240
Look at you.

424
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,240
What's wrong?

425
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,830
I'm not even married yet.

426
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,550
It makes me sad, too.

427
00:24:55,920 --> 00:24:58,850
What's there to be sad about?
I'm just happy about it.

428
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:00,000
You silly child.

429
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:01,830
Happy.

430
00:25:04,110 --> 00:25:04,750
Jiangyan.

431
00:25:05,000 --> 00:25:06,110
Listen.

432
00:25:07,070 --> 00:25:07,830
Since you were little,

433
00:25:07,830 --> 00:25:08,630
you've always

434
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,440
liked to keep everything

435
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:13,340
buried in your heart
without saying it out loud.

436
00:25:13,510 --> 00:25:15,510
Now you're starting your own family.

437
00:25:15,510 --> 00:25:16,480
I just hope

438
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:19,160
you'll be happy every day from now on.

439
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,350
Okay?

440
00:25:23,830 --> 00:25:25,350
I will, Mom.

441
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:28,940
Why are you crying?

442
00:25:29,310 --> 00:25:29,830
Mom.

443
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,660
You've been the best to me.

444
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:34,310
You've been good to me, too.

445
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,400
My good child.

446
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:39,440
I'll always be with you.

447
00:25:50,770 --> 00:25:52,750
[Ancestral Hall
of the Liu, Wen, and Qin Families]

448
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:55,880
Today, we're holding the Longwan Logistics
shareholders meeting.

449
00:25:55,880 --> 00:25:57,400
The board of directors has already sent

450
00:25:57,400 --> 00:26:00,160
written notices to all shareholders
according to the bylaws.

451
00:26:00,160 --> 00:26:02,590
The number of attendees
exceeds two-thirds.

452
00:26:02,590 --> 00:26:04,920
So the meeting will proceed as scheduled.

453
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:06,800
Now, let me introduce...

454
00:26:06,830 --> 00:26:07,690
That's enough.

455
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:10,640
Let's skip the formalities.

456
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,270
That's fine.

457
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:19,000
I'm sure everyone knows

458
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:20,720
why we're here today.

459
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:23,790
Liu Tianye,

460
00:26:24,750 --> 00:26:27,280
as the General Manager
of Longwan Logistics,

461
00:26:27,350 --> 00:26:29,880
has been making unilateral decisions
during his tenure

462
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:32,540
and hasn't fought
for our long-term interests.

463
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,090
On the contrary,

464
00:26:35,270 --> 00:26:38,000
he has brought many bad practices
to the company.

465
00:26:38,830 --> 00:26:40,350
So today I propose

466
00:26:41,200 --> 00:26:43,200
that we elect a new General Manager.

467
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,400
If you trust me,

468
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:46,980
please vote for me.

469
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:48,440
I'm sorry, Mom. I...

470
00:26:48,440 --> 00:26:50,440
I'd like to take up
a bit of everyone's time.

471
00:26:50,440 --> 00:26:51,000
Just now...

472
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:52,590
You don't need to say anything.

473
00:26:52,590 --> 00:26:55,250
Let's proceed according
to the company bylaws.

474
00:26:57,680 --> 00:26:58,240
Right.

475
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:01,610
According to the company bylaws,

476
00:27:02,550 --> 00:27:04,000
as long as there are enough votes,

477
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,060
one can be elected.

478
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:10,060
I believe I'm more suitable
to lead Longwan Logistics.

479
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,120
So this time,

480
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:16,070
I will participate in the election.

481
00:27:19,200 --> 00:27:19,960
Jiangyan,

482
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:21,880
what are you doing?

483
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:22,480
Mom,

484
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:24,680
trust me.

485
00:27:25,680 --> 00:27:27,610
I've made thorough preparations.

486
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,310
Everyone.

487
00:27:35,880 --> 00:27:36,660
I know that

488
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:39,200
many things have happened
in Longwan recently

489
00:27:39,200 --> 00:27:40,860
that have affected all of you.

490
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:43,590
I've assembled a professional legal team

491
00:27:43,590 --> 00:27:45,790
to work with me to resolve these issues.

492
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:48,030
I will definitely provide you
with answers.

493
00:27:48,030 --> 00:27:49,750
But Longwan
has more fundamental problems

494
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:51,210
that need to be addressed.

495
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:53,570
The company's future development

496
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,920
requires reform.

497
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,140
We must keep up with the times.

498
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,960
We must learn from our mistakes.

499
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:01,000
I promise you all here

500
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:03,200
that I will do my utmost

501
00:28:03,590 --> 00:28:05,200
to protect everyone's interests

502
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:07,000
and lead Longwan on a clean path,

503
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,930
away from all controversy.

504
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:12,000
Please vote for me.

505
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:29,050
I vote for Jiangyan.

506
00:28:30,590 --> 00:28:31,880
Jiangyan is well-educated,

507
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:32,640
capable,

508
00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:34,330
and detail-oriented.

509
00:28:34,440 --> 00:28:35,700
Just as she mentioned,

510
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:37,070
she has already assembled

511
00:28:37,070 --> 00:28:38,600
a professional legal team.

512
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:41,000
This provides the company

513
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:43,720
with strong legal protection
for the future.

514
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,250
As for me,

515
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:45,200
today,

516
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:49,000
I resign from all my positions
at Longwan Logistics.

517
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,420
Please vote for Jiangyan.

518
00:28:51,920 --> 00:28:52,520
Thank you.

519
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:10,170
Xinrui Group
took over Qiao Defu's business—

520
00:29:11,270 --> 00:29:13,530
You must have been the middleman, right?

521
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:16,280
And those things that happened
to Qiao Defu

522
00:29:17,110 --> 00:29:18,510
were also related to you.

523
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:22,510
I got to know Qiao Defu in the first place

524
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:24,070
just so that

525
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:26,670
I could collaborate
with Xinrui Group one day.

526
00:29:28,510 --> 00:29:30,440
Have you ever seen this much money?

527
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:35,080
If I had this money earlier,

528
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:37,550
Longwan wouldn't have been bullied,

529
00:29:37,550 --> 00:29:39,680
and our loved ones wouldn't have left.

530
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:42,950
This is the future I want,

531
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:46,200
a future where we're not pushed around.

532
00:29:46,550 --> 00:29:48,110
Everything you see now

533
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,520
is what gives me confidence.

534
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:56,360
I have a buddy called Ran.

535
00:29:59,590 --> 00:30:01,320
He was in the trading business.

536
00:30:01,510 --> 00:30:02,440
He was arrested.

537
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:07,060
You were the informant, weren't you?

538
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,240
It was me.

539
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,070
Not just Ran,

540
00:30:12,550 --> 00:30:14,610
I have plenty of other evidence, too.

541
00:30:15,790 --> 00:30:16,590
Smuggling.

542
00:30:16,880 --> 00:30:17,940
Money laundering.

543
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,330
Illegal transactions.

544
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:22,550
Regarding
this major anti-smuggling operation,

545
00:30:22,550 --> 00:30:24,830
you've legally cut all ties,

546
00:30:26,590 --> 00:30:28,590
but as for other related documents,

547
00:30:28,960 --> 00:30:30,820
I have kept backups of all of them.

548
00:30:37,720 --> 00:30:38,720
A law graduate...

549
00:30:39,160 --> 00:30:39,890
Impressive.

550
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:43,550
So you, a law graduate,
target your own family members, huh?

551
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:45,960
So, how are you going
to deal with all of this?

552
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:46,890
Give them to Mom?

553
00:30:49,440 --> 00:30:51,040
Or will you give them to Feng?

554
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,240
Tianye.

555
00:30:56,070 --> 00:30:56,750
I know

556
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,310
you've sacrificed everything

557
00:30:58,310 --> 00:31:00,110
for this family and for Longwan.

558
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:02,250
But wrong is wrong.

559
00:31:02,370 --> 00:31:03,800
And the law is the law.

560
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,850
What you are doing right now is a crime.

561
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:09,800
You'll lead Longwan
into an abyss of no return.

562
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:17,590
This evidence...

563
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:22,080
I can choose not to hand it over.

564
00:31:24,160 --> 00:31:25,090
What do you mean?

565
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:29,900
I won't let Mom
take Longwan back to the past,

566
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:34,090
but I won't let you drag Longwan
into the gutter, either.

567
00:31:34,310 --> 00:31:36,110
At this shareholders' meeting,

568
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,810
I want you to support me.

569
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:39,880
From today onwards,

570
00:31:40,590 --> 00:31:42,070
Longwan must stay clean.

571
00:31:45,200 --> 00:31:46,880
Now let's begin the vote.

572
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,920
Those in favor of Wen Jiangyan

